snippet.title: Battlefield 3™ Premium Launch Trailer Official E3 2012
snippet.description: Battlefield 3 Premium members will get all five game-changing themed expansion packs combined with two week's early access. You will also receive a host of exclusive in-game items including the ACB-90 knife, a set of Premium dog tags, and soldier and weapon camos - all complemented by unique Battlelog features, Double XP weekends, and other exclusive events and videos.
